To alleviate the nation's energy crisis Bangladesh adopted daylight saving
time last June. The government [has
decided](http://www.bdnews24.com/details.php?cid=2&id=149526&hb=top) today to
turn back the clock on the 31st December midnight. _Omi Azad_ at _Micro
Reality Bites_ [asks](http://omiazad.wordpress.com/2009/12/24/483/) when
exactly Bangladeshis will be celebrating the new year then?

